Nobody paid any attention to them until it was far too late.
The coronerâ€™s inquest or, more specifically, the graphic news reporting of it is what horrified readers and flooded both the Ottawa Citizen and Ottawa Journal editors with letters from furious readers. See â€œLetters to the Editor Slam Reporting Slam Lurid Reportingâ€ at the bottom of this article.
